{"tid":1567960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回歸初心］不分化、不篤灰、不割蓆、不抹黑、不捉鬼！","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:10:44.000Z","uid":156865,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"b32867999e6d0b4290e342f798dbb869a4429cf9","tid":1567960,"uid":156865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"呢排互相指責嘅post出左黎，周圍喺度互篤，<br />\n就用今日淘大叫唔叫人做例子 已經爭吵一餐<br />\n將好多重要同行動嘅post洗走晒<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況真係好似2014年啊！<br />\n大家要知分化我地就會輸，我地勢弱言輕，只有團結先有可能贏到！<br />\n麻煩手足正負評前、留言前都諗清諗楚<br />\n<br />\n請緊記<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力！<br />\n不分化、不篤灰、不割蓆、不抹黑、不捉鬼！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請手動轉貼洗板，一定要令每個手足知道，<br />\n結束分化！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"41d8d3bb6301e0ae884e192bcf71a43e92e11384","tid":1567960,"uid":156865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"自推20個（1/20）"},{"pid":"d7ebc84bcb54544eb51b6b53b1a98c581d1afe84","tid":1567960,"uid":156865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"自推20個（2/20）"},{"pid":"8fa1a67670a741c3c294dfa3f6f8336a7bd8cf65","tid":1567960,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0747d16937a3e7ffba617bd501fe690c84b53c6a","tid":1567960,"uid":8028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:54:49.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山各自努力 <br />\n<br />\n唱歌 勇武 和理非 啱就去做<br />\n<br />\n分化post善用不推文"},{"pid":"83e0fd207