捉唔完<br />\n與其捉鬼 不如加強自身更加有效"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"O明白"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:12:11.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n大家互相扶持 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好比鬼分化"},{"pid":"3bd6564575d490a33e69bf0c0a35485d7896e564","tid":1567960,"uid":193215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:13:07.000Z","msg":"唔好再講「再點點點就割」<br />\n唔好再講「再點點點就輸喇」<br />\n<br />\n今時今日去到而家局勢，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武、文宣、軍心、士氣、團結，缺一不可</span></span>，唔好再講唱歌會輸，唔出去幫手會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋從未受過軍事訓練，能夠做到而家咁已經好好，弱勢一方最緊要係避重就輕，唔好送頭，唔好打無準備嘅仗，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「預則立，不預則廢」</span></span>，突發出動只會俾狗有機可乘，呢三個月以來已經有好多前線勇武巴絲受傷同被捕，我哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係唔做無把握嘅仗，而係唔好做無計劃過嘅仗</span></span>，唔好因為對家做乜就衝動出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸於香港</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b283b16380605084445b67a249fe13141f3945c8","tid":1567960,"uid":267912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:13:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64c67ff20d416a3f4af5f8f7be0942a1776d1a21","tid":1567960,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43656cebdae06365023cf5aa9f27bc4195d1424d","tid":1567960,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c5213dc7583ed6df5b0cf6b6a1484f3997550eb","tid":1567960,"uid":156865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bd6564575d490a33e69bf0c0a35485d7896e564","tid":1567960,"uid"